 equal parts on both dust abundances\nand grain sizes distributions for the scalings investigated in this paper.\nHigher dust abundances and smaller grain sizes cause larger departures from the\nradiative cooling (i.e. with no dust) model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 17 Aug 2008 21:40:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
