ch up with an abrupt change in the\nstimulus.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Aug 2008 06:27:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Apr 2009 15:34:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 4 Apr 2009 10:38:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-04-12"}
